Description: Handle of pottery transport amphora. Rectangular(?) stamp
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p. 32, 11. Name, Timotheos. He is not otherwise known to omit a month name.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.1108)
